des: KLCK 1400 was the first Radio Station Licensed in Klickitat County going on the air in 1984 in Goldendale, Washington. Today we feature a talk radio format with CBS News at the top of every hour. Local news and a local call in talk show \"Hotline\" Monday through Friday mornings at 8:35. Weekday Programs include America In The Morning, The Doug Stephan, Glenn Beck, Dave Ramsey, Lars Larson, John Batchelor & Red Eye Radio. Find us at klck1400.com. We are a Gorge Country Media Station.
